030package javax.measure.test;
031
032import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.*;
033
034import javax.measure.Dimension;
035import org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeEach;
036import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;
037
038public class DimensionTest {
039    private Dimension sut;
040
041    @BeforeEach
042    public void init() {
043        sut = TestDimension.getInstance();
044    }
045
046    @Test
047    public void testGetInstance() {
048        Dimension dim = TestDimension.getInstance();
049        assertNotNull(dim);
050    }
051
052    @Test
053    public void testMultiply() {
054        Dimension dim = TestDimension.getInstance();
055        Dimension result = sut.multiply(dim);
056        assertNotNull(result);
057    }
058
059    @Test
060    public void testDivide() {
061        Dimension dim = TestDimension.getInstance();
062        Dimension result = sut.divide(dim);
063        assertNotNull(result);
064    }
065
066    @Test
067    public void testPow() {
068        Dimension result = sut.pow(2);
069        assertNotNull(result);
070    }
071
072    @Test
073    public void testRoot() {
074        Dimension result = sut.root(2);
075        assertNotNull(result);
076    }
077
078    @Test
079    public void testGetProductDimensions() {
080        assertNotNull(sut.getBaseDimensions());
081        assertEquals(1, sut.getBaseDimensions().size());
082    }
083
084}
